<h2 class="bold font-l">Gumball loves Penny</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Darwin asks Gumball if he wants Penny to be his date for Rachel's party </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="fc4udf" data-video-descrip="The instant Cricket first sets eyes on Gabriella, he is immediately lovestruck." data-video-title="Cricket meets Gabriella" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/fc4udf_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/fc4udf.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CrushFilter" data-video-tropename="Crush Filter" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/BigCityGreens" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/fc4udf.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Cricket meets G...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="2q18nv" data-video-descrip="Hiccup has a crush on Astrid. Can you tell?" data-video-title="Hiccup Loves Astrid" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/2q18nv_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/2q18nv.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CrushFilter" data-video-tropename="Crush Filter" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/HowToTrainYourDragon" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/2q18nv.jpg">
